Note:
aott/analysis/call_graph/optimizer.runa
Call-Based Optimization Module for AOTT Runtime Performance

This module provides call graph-based optimizations for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Aggressive function inlining strategies
- Call devirtualization and specialization
- Tail call optimization
- Function cloning for specialization
- Call site optimization and caching
- Interprocedural constant propagation
- Dead function elimination
- Function outlining for code size
- Call chain flattening
- Polymorphic inline cache optimization
- Speculative devirtualization
- Call frequency-based code layout
- Function fusion and splitting
- Cross-function register allocation
- Call overhead reduction techniques
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

